    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253460/extras/2154f9d29339226e32bf40fb961ba383.avif?t=1758741476\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253460/extras_big/2154f9d29339226e32bf40fb961ba383.avif?t=1758741476 width=800 height=450 /></span><strong>Escape from Box City</strong> is a lighthearted 3D platformer designed by a 7-year-old art director, offering a playful and creative adventure for all ages. The game takes place in a sprawling city made entirely of cardboard boxes, where players can choose from a variety of quirky, clay-animated characters to explore the world. The objective? To navigate through tunnels, leap across towering platforms, and find hidden items that will help you make your great escape from the city!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This kid-friendly adventure focuses on the fun of exploration and discovery without combat or violence. With a heavy emphasis on humor, imagination, and problem-solving, the game presents a colorful world full of surprises around every corner. It’s perfect for younger players and families looking for a silly, engaging, and non-violent platforming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253460/extras/9b54b2c6bceb1bcaa562306638111408.avif?t=1758741476\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253460/extras_big/9b54b2c6bceb1bcaa562306638111408.avif?t=1758741476 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
